{
  "stem": "11882.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And for weeks, we had no students.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that moment, I telephoned Herr Martine Sachs down in Silesia, down in Hirschberg-- a beautiful town, still beautiful.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Today it's a Polish area.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went down there to see Herr Sachs.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was a relative of relatives of relatives in Rochester.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had said that his little daughter, he wanted her to learn English.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he might have to go to America, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And would this lady from Hamburg come over to his home in Silesia?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I telephoned him when we had no work to do and no pay, of course, in Hamburg, and said, how would it be if I come now?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And his family were there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they said, oh yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That would be fine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "What I didn't know was that he, too, had been arrested, that he was in a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So I packed up and went through Germany without much knowledge of German.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the Germans behaved in a very orderly fashion, no terrorism on the streets like we have today in these bad days.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Hitler ran a good shop.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Everything was-- you were dumped into a concentration camp if you said, boo, almost.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And everybody was very orderly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You could walk on the streets in the middle of the night almost, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I arrived at this difficult place.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It took me, oh, a long time to get there-- transfer in Berlin, transfer underway, and finally got to Silesia.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And as I arrived, I telephoned from the station-- I think it was late in the evening-- and said I've just come.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shall I take-- and he said, take a taxi, so much I could understand.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Take a taxi and come over to our house.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
